* Iron Raptor looked towards Symphony, nodding. But then felt a slight wind 
pick up, her cape flapping slightly while her hair moved against her 
shoulder-plated.
She would have taken it as simply one which was picked up from the south and 
was carried across the field but it had a sort of...peaceful feeling to it, 
but whatever Prowl and Eypon were speaking about was lost to her.
The battle was over and now it was time to repair and get to work.
Iron Raptor held the kitten in her arms, taking a few steps towards the CF 
and glancing down at him. It was time to collect a little peace of her own.
She simply smiled down at him and continued on her way, hearing Prowl ask 
her opinion on whatever idea Eypon and himself were having. She had cought 
small snatches of it but there were other things to do right now then start 
something else that would complicate matters at the moment.
She would hear what they had to say, just not right now.*

" Tell me later."

* Iron Raptor looked over her shoulder towards the remainder of the Maximals 
which were behind her, motioning with her chin for them to follow. It was 
time for repairs.
She opened a comm to Hysteria.*

" How's the lockdown going?"
